.Tn MDS RPC
request service
.It Ic mstiosthr
Timed
.Tn I/O
stats updater thread
.It Ic msusklndplthr Ns Ar %d
Lustre userland socket poll thread
.It Ic everyone
All threads (default, where applicable)
.El
